title: Camp WeWow Magic Week Day 4
description:
It's Magic Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're using science to magically stick a straw through a potato!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/experiment-stick-a-straw-through-a-potato for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share!
